== Tarakalt d unzwi ==
Teṭṭaf tsga n Sus-Massa iwtta d tsga n [[Tasga n Mrrakc-Asfi|Mṛṛakc-Asfi]] ɣ ugafa, d tsga n [[Tasga n Glmim-Asif Nun|Glmim-Asif Nun]] ɣ unẓul, d tsga n [[Tasga n Dṛɛa-Tafilalt|Dṛɛa-Tafilalt]] ɣ ugmuḍ, amma ɣ utaram ar taggʷ f [[Agaraw anaṭlas|ugaraw anaṭlas]]. Tasga y'ad gis kigan n timẓlay tirakaln zund idrarn n [[Aṭlas mqqurn|waṭlas mqqurn]] (Adrar n dern) d [[Aṭlas mẓẓiyn|wad imẓẓiyn]] d idrarn n [[Idrarn n Bani|Bani]] d [[Idrarn n Warkziz|Warkziz]] lli gis izrayn, gis ula afa n idrarn n tfriqt ugafa ad t-igan d adrar n [[tubqal]], yili gis [[asif n Sus]] lli d izrin f uzaɣar n Sus imqqurn, d [[asif n Massa]] ula ntta d wiyyaḍ. Tettussan Sus Massa s taganin n [[Argan|trganin]] lli gis illan, d [[Tagant|taganin]] lli illan ɣ tsga-ad lkmn ar 19% ɣ taganin n tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]]. Tajumma n tsga tlkm ar 53,789 km².<ref>Tadwayrit n tfllaḥt n [http://chambreagriculturesm.com/ar/%D9%85%D9%88%D9%86%D9%88%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%8A%D8%A7/#:~:text=%D8%AA%D8%AA%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%B2%20%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%A9%20%D8%B9%D9%85%D9%88%D9%85%D8%A7%20%D8%A8%D9%85%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AE%20%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%81,600%20%D9%85%D9%84%D9%85%20%D9%81%D9%8A%20%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B7%D9%84%D8%B3%20%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%B1. tsga n Sus Massa]</ref> Anzwi n tsga iḥma ɣ ugnz macc iga ɛadi ɣ taman yill, ur aɣ bdda iṭṭar [[Anẓar|unẓaṛ]] ɣ tsga-ad. Kra n twal ar ikkat tuqqurt nɣ d azaɣ lli iẓḍaṛ ad ilkm azmz-nns ar sin isggʷasn. Taflwit ad illan ddaw-as ar takka umlan f tirɣi nɣd lḥma d uṣmmiḍ ɣ tmdint n [[Agadir]] da igan tamaẓunt n tsga.
