== Tuṣkiwt tanaddaw ==
[[Afaylu:Panoramica stade Agadir.jpg|thumb|238x238px|[[Abaraz n Adrar]] illan ɣ tmdint n [[Agadir|Ugadir]].]]
[[Azagʷz agraɣlan n Ugadir]] (Azagʷz n Lmasira n Umgadir) iga yan uzagʷz illan ɣ tmdint tamɣribit n ugadir d nttan ay'swurrin ɣ tsga n Sus-Massa. Yaggug azagʷz ad f tuẓẓumt n tmdint f 20 kilomitr (taman Tmsiya), yaẓ i ubrid anamur 10. Iga azagʷz wis-kraḍ da akk imqqurn ɣ tmazirt n Lmɣrib zɣ nnaḥit n inmudda. Ittuyṛẓam ɣ usggʷas n 1991 d iẓḍar ad yasi 3 id mlyun n inmudda<ref>[https://www.flightsfrom.com/AGA Flightsfrom.com] - Azagz n Ugadir.</ref>.

Tasga y'ad yan ubrbrid ka gis izrayn ad-t igan d ubrbrid n Tigmmi tumlult-Agadir. Ibridn inamurn lli illan ɣ tsga gan tn: Abrid anamur 1, Abrid anamur 7, Abrid anamur 10, Abrid anamur 11, Abrid anamur 17.<ref>[http://www.sgg.gov.ma/BO/Ar/2018/BO_6677_Ar.pdf?ver=2018-05-29-155624-277 Tizlit tamaddudt - uṭṭun 6677 n wass 28 n may 2015 - tasna tis-22-23-25.]</ref>

[[Abaraz n Adrar|Abaraz mqqurn n Adrar]] (Abaraz mqqurn n Ugadir) ay'gan abaraz n tkurt n uḍar nna illan ɣ tmdint n Ugadir, nnuṛẓmn iggura nɣd iflwan nns ass n 11 n wayyur wis-mraw n usggʷas n 2013. Illa ubaraz ad ɣ wayda n tamawast n tiɛɛurma d tunnunt d tbidd f uswurri nns tamssurt tanamurt n usnulfu d uswuddu n ibarazn (SONARGES). Ar isbrrak ɣilad ubaraz ad timnyugarin n trabbut n [[Talḥasant n Ugadir]], d lbɛḍ n twal tin Ulampik Dcayra.

== Tadamsa ==
[[Afaylu:Arganier (2).JPG|thumb|200x200px|Yat [[Argan|targant]] ɣ tasga n Sus-Massa.]]

=== Tafllaḥt ===

Tasga n Sus-Massa ay'gan tasga tamzwarut ɣ usifḍ n tismmamin (llimun, d lmanḍaṛin, d navil d lḥamḍ) d lbawakir gr tsgiwin n Lmɣrib kullutn.<ref name=":1">[https://www.soussmassa.ma/system/files_force/publicaltion_files/R%C3%A9gion%20Souss%20Massa%20en%20chiffre%20Ar%201.pdf? Tasga n Sus Massa s izwiln] - Soussmassa.ma <small>[PDF]</small></ref> 85% n lbawakir d 65% n tismmamin d 15% n ukfay d ɣayli t-id iwalan d 86% n iyafutn n wargan llid itsifiḍ [[Lmɣrib]] s brra ar ttackan zɣ tsga n Sus-Massa, gis 650.000 ṭonn n tismmamin d 1.2 id mlyun ṭonn n lxḍʷṛt nna d tsifiḍ, nna gis illan ula tamaḍact d taxsayt d bṭaṭa d [[Aẓalim|uẓalim]]. Ḥ Sus-Massa uggar n 5.371.000 hiktar n wakal d tiɣula iɛdln i tfllaḥt, 475.000 hiktar ka s swurrin middn d 158.433 ka das ittuskar yigm. Afars amsmun n tismmamin ilkm ar 700.000 ṭonn d 1.665.000 ṭonn n lxḍʷṛt d 28.086 n tifiyya tazggʷɣt d 223.5 id mlyun iṭṛu n [[Akʷfay|ukfay]], ɣayad kullut ɣ 33 wass n twuri.<ref name=":1" /> Illa ɣ tsga n Sus-Massa 180 kilomiṭṛ n yill, nna d ittusafaḍn iyafutn nns 137.830 ṭonn, nna d ittawi 1450 aɣrrabu abldi d 465 asaḥili d 223 n yill agafay. Ar tssufḍ tsga n Sus-Massa waḥdut 50% n iyafutn tylant ɣ tizznbilin n Lmɣrib, ar swurrin ɣ yigr ad 490.000 n yan zɣ tmazirt kullut, 72.000 gisn at'gan tarwa n tsga.<ref name=":1" />[[Afaylu:Secteur Touristique, Agadir 80000, Morocco - panoramio (18).jpg|thumb|Marina taman yill n [[Agadir|Ugadir]].]]
=== Tamguri ===
[[Afaylu:MAP Paris Fibules 04032012 1.jpg|thumb|132x132px|[[Taẓṛẓit]] tasusit tamaziɣt tamɣribit.]]
[[Afaylu:TAROUDANNT defensive wall (js).jpg|thumb|135x135px|Imi n Tarɣunt ɣ [[Tarudant]].]]
Ḥ tsga n Sus-Massa 440 ifrdas imgurann, tugt nns imma tzdi d tirmt nɣd timttawin tikimiyn nɣd lbni n lbaṭwaṛ. Ḥ tmdint n [[Agadir|ugadir]] illa yan udɣar ilelli (aḥuṛṛi) ibdan tawuri nns ɣ usggʷas n 2019 s 64 hiktar,<ref name=":1" /> d ar ttinin mas tufa ad tlkm 300 hiktar ɣ yimal. Llan daɣ idɣarn imgurann yaḍnin ɣ Anẓa d Tasila d Wlad tayma d Sidi Bibi d [[Tiznit]] d [[Tarudant]] d [[Inzggan]]. Illa udɣar alujistik yan ɣ [[Ayt Mllul]] wayya ɣ [[Tagadirt]].<ref name=":1" /> Tasga y'ad gis Tiknupark d tamdint n usllwu iwalan i [[tasdawit n Bnu Zuhṛ]]. Teṭṭaf tamguri tabldit yat tilalt bahra istawhman, acku ixdm gis 40.000 yan d ar tssifiḍ 15 id mlyun n ddrhm. Llan 5 n wammasn n usmuttg azzulan d 120 n tmyawasin n tamguri tabldit nna itɛdaln yilm d ttub d uckkuḍ d tizuzaf d ufrur d ɣaylli n tẓṛbay d idukan d kra kullu. Zɣ wanawn n tamguri tabldit nna s bahra ttussan tsga y'ad tlla tamguri n idukan d taẓṛbit tawawzgitit d tiẓṛẓay.

=== Tamallayt ===
[[Afaylu:الواحة.jpeg|thumb|173x173px|Azaɣar n [[Ṭaṭa]].]]
Tasga n Sus-Massa ar sis tackan uggar n mlyun n imlulluyn ɣ usggʷas, nna d git izrayn 5 id mlyun n yiḍan (amagut n diyiḍ) ɣ tamuttrt ɣ 31 tassutin tqriban. Igr ad ar gis txdamn uggar n 120.000 n yan d ar iskcam i tsga 20 id mlyar n ddrhm kraygat usggʷas. Tamallayt tagnsant tɣʷi gis 43% d ɣaylli iɣaman gan imlulluyn id ittackan zɣ [[Fransa]] (21%), [[Lalman]] (14.5%), [[Nngliz]] (12%) d [[Hulanda|Hulanḍa]] (2%). Illa bzzaf ma'yttuyskarn ɣ tsga n Sus-Massa, zund ad tftut ad tbḥḥrt ɣ [[Agadir|Ugadir]], [[Imswan]], [[Taɣazut]] nɣd [[Tamri]]. Tamallayt n idrarn swa ucffal nɣd s lppikalat. Tamallayt tadlsant ɣ [[Tarudant]], [[Tiznit]] d [[Tafrawt]], tiggit n izaɣarn n Ṭaṭa lli bahra iqburn. Aradab ɣ yill nɣd tawada ɣ ammas n Sus-Massa<ref name=":1" />. Imlulluyn llid ittackan s Sus-Massa ẓḍarn ad aggʷn f ugadaz n Lḥdd, tasnniɣt tamaziɣt, Marina, [[Agadir Uflla]], lpark lli n ttamasiḥ nɣd lpark n ḍufan n [[Agadir|Ugadir]], Igudar n [[Actukn|Wactukn]]-Ayt Baha, Asif n Paradiz ɣ Immuzzar Idawtanan, iɣʷrban n Tarudant, igʷjjifn n Tiyut, Zzawaya d iɣrman iqburn, nnuqac iqburn d ifran n Ṭaṭa d iẓṛan iẓṛwaln n Tafrawt.

